bradleyross.swing

Class SwingTimer

  • java.lang.Object
    • bradleyross.swing.SwingTimer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable

    public class SwingTimer
extends Object
implements Runnable
    This Swing demo creates a JPanel component and randomly moves a red dot within the panel when triggered by a timer.

    Try changing the size of the window to see how it affects the relationship between the button and the panel where the graphics are generated.

    The Timer object was replaced with a Timer object.

    Author:
    Bradley Ross
